article.description: Conner Toolson had 21 points as Utah Valley topped UMKC 71-64 in the quarterfinals of the Western Athletic Conference Tourney on Thursday night.
article.headline: Toolson scores 21 to lift Utah Valley over UMKC 71-64
article.linkText: Toolson scores 21 to lift Utah Valley over UMKC 71-64
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- Conner Toolson had 21 points as Utah Valley topped UMKC 71-64 in the quarterfinals of the Western Athletic Conference Tourney on Thursday night. Richard Harward had 15 points for Utah Valley (24-8). Isaiah White added six rebounds. Jake Toolson had seven rebounds for Utah Valley. Xavier Bishop had 17 points for the Kangaroos (11-21). Jamel Allen added 12 points.
